displayName: City of Orosh in the Mountains, House of Guard Doron

parameters:
Guard Drone: If you have any troubles, please call out to
the city guards.

Guard Drone: Thank you for coming! Let me explain the
details of the request.

Clea: An infiltration investigation into the arena... is
that what you're saying?

Guard Drone: It is an infiltration into a secret arena that
is said to be located in Dromos, not the Pizma Arena.

Guard Drone: My father, Cleos, had attempted infiltration,
but his whereabouts have been unknown for several months...

Priestess Sophia: As a condition for accepting this request,
there was a requirement to win at the Pizma Arena. Why is
that?

Guard Drone: It is said that in order to participate in the
secret arena, one must be recognized by the scoutman.

Guard Drone: They are watching the Pizma Arena. You all
should be their scouting targets.
Clea: Understood, I will head to Dromos first.

Guard Drone: Thank you! I also want to infiltrate the city
of Dromos.

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Oros Region/Golden City
Dromos\c[0]

Guard Drone: We can only rely on all of you. Please take
care of us.
Guard Drone: Father... I'm glad you're safe!

Guard Drone: Thank you very much. I will proceed with the
payment of the reward.
Guard Cleos: I would also like to express my gratitude.

Clea: Thank you very much, Phoni-san. We wouldn't have been
able to resolve it without you.
Voice Priestess Phoni: No... I'm glad I could be of help.

Voice Priestess Phoni: I feel like my relationship with my
father has returned, even if it's just a little... really,
just a little.

Voice Priestess Phoni: If you ever have any troubles, please
don't hesitate to reach out to me, okay?
実績 暗黒の舞台へようこそ
実績 地下闘技場の挑戦者

Guard Drone: My father stopped the investigation of the
underground arena. There's a possibility that the Senate is
involved, so we have to be careful.

Guard Cleos: The darkness of Dromos is deeper than I
thought. Be careful not to get too involved.
